South Korea

11:12.004 --> 11:13.739 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
is indicative of this.

11:13.839 --> 11:15.608 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so I think South Korea is
stuck in the
middle.

11:15.708 --> 11:21.347 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And given that,
with South
Korea stuck in the middle, John
Merrill, how

11:21.447 --> 11:25.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
