The Trump administration has
been making provocative
statements.

11:32.091 --> 11:38.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN MERRILL: I think people
should try to
cool the situation to the extent
possible.

11:38.497 --> 11:43.803 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
There's going to be a new
government in Seoul
think on the 9th of next month.

11:43.903 --> 11:44.937 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: They have an
election coming
up.

11:45.037 --> 11:46.038 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN MERRILL: Yes.

11:46.138 --> 11:48.607 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And the president will be
installed immediately.

11:48.708 --> 11:53.646 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think it's a little unseemly
to rush a THAAD
battery in, in the dead of
night.

11:53.746 --> 11:56.415 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: This is the
missile defense
system.

