(CROSSTALK)

11:57.483 --> 11:58.384 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN MERRILL: Yes.

11:58.484 --> 11:59.385 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

11:59.485 --> 12:00.386 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

12:00.486 --> 12:01.754 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

12:01.854 --> 12:03.689 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there's serious questions
about whether
the thing works.

12:03.789 --> 12:05.291 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
