12:06.826 --> 12:08.527 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What about that?

12:08.627 --> 12:12.598 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BALBINA HWANG: I'm far less
concerned about
