surreptitious.

12:12.698 --> 12:14.467 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think these plans were already
in place.

12:14.567 --> 12:18.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What concerns me is that, on the
one hand,
we're trying to send the message
to China

12:18.204 --> 12:20.706 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
