serious.

12:20.806 --> 12:24.577 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the other hand, at the same
time this is
all happening, and Secretary
Tillerson and

12:24.677 --> 12:29.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump are emphasizing
