herring.

13:56.402 --> 13:59.071 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think what's actually very
critical is this.

13:59.171 --> 14:03.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
All the U.S. presidents have at
some point
understood that they will try to
negotiate

14:03.976 --> 14:05.144 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
