are the key,
and that every regional player
has to be involved,

14:36.475 --> 14:38.410 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and most importantly South
Korea.

14:38.510 --> 14:43.983 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think now what's happening
