all of our attention.

15:30.829 --> 15:31.897 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN MERRILL: That's for sure.

15:31.997 --> 15:33.799 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We thank both of
you coming
in.

15:33.899 --> 15:37.002 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I know we're going to be to
continuing
to report on it, and you're
going to continue

15:37.102 --> 15:38.003 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to watch it.

15:38.103 --> 15:39.405 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
John Merrill, Balbina Hwang,
