15:39.505 --> 15:41.440 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BALBINA HWANG: Thank you.

15:41.540 --> 15:49.815 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JOHN MERRILL: Thank you, Judy.

