16:24.717 --> 16:29.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: He is trying to prove to
the world
that Egypt is still safe, no
matter what terrorism

16:29.588 --> 16:31.824 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is trying to do in our country.

16:31.924 --> 16:36.061 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Just three
weeks ago, 45
people died when the Islamic
State bombed

16:36.161 --> 16:39.465 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Christian churches in two
