on Palm Sunday.

16:39.565 --> 16:45.137 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And, in December, an ISIS
suicide bomber killed
25 people at Cairo's main Coptic
Christian

16:45.237 --> 16:46.805 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
