17:59.211 --> 18:03.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's something that has really
plagued the
Christian community in Egypt for
a very long

18:03.715 --> 18:05.451 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
