18:05.551 --> 18:08.787 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Under Hosni Mubarak, the
president who was
overthrown in 2011, there had
been violence

18:08.887 --> 18:10.622 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
