18:10.722 --> 18:14.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When the military took over in
Egypt in 2011,
there was violence against
Christians.

18:14.159 --> 18:18.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When the Muslim Brotherhood was
in charge
for a brief moment in Egypt,
there was violence

18:18.163 --> 18:19.998 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
against Christians.

18:20.099 --> 18:23.068 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
