18:25.037 --> 18:27.906 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Just to put it
in a little
context, what's the standing of
Christians

18:28.006 --> 18:29.842 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
