Church is the
world's oldest Christian church.

18:47.826 --> 18:51.730 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the Coptic Christians are
indigenous to
Egypt.

18:51.830 --> 18:58.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
