19:00.472 --> 19:06.478 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So Christians are really an
inextricable part
of the fabric of Egyptian life.

19:06.578 --> 19:12.551 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The problem is, particularly
since the 1970s,
that society has become
increasingly Islamized,

19:12.651 --> 19:17.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
