as the other,
and there have been a lot of
attempts to delegitimize

19:17.422 --> 19:18.957 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
them, discriminate against them.

19:19.057 --> 19:21.527 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And now we're seeing acts of
violence against
them.

19:21.627 --> 19:25.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, what's the
strategic
value for ISIS to carry out
these acts of

19:25.697 --> 19:27.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
