and Christian churches is two
things.

19:43.916 --> 19:47.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
First, they want to delegitimize
the Egyptian
regime.

19:47.586 --> 19:50.856 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
After all, President Sisi came
to power promising
stability.

19:50.956 --> 19:55.427 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And so these kinds of
spectacular acts of
violence merely underscore his
inability to

19:55.527 --> 19:57.329 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
provide that stability.

19:57.429 --> 20:01.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The other thing they want to do
is, they want
to paint the government as
somehow not just

20:01.934 --> 20:03.936 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
