21:47.205 --> 21:51.176 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, one hopes that those kinds
of messages
will diffuse throughout the
Muslim world.

21:51.276 --> 21:53.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
Tarek Masoud
from Harvard's Kennedy School of
Government,

21:53.945 --> 21:55.447 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
thanks so much.

21:55.547 --> 22:02.788 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TAREK MASOUD: Thank you, Hari.

22:02.888 --> 22:10.062 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Stay with us.

22:10.162 --> 22:14.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Coming up on the "NewsHour":
Mark Shields
and David Brooks analyze the
first 100 days

22:14.166 --> 22:21.740 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the Trump administration;
